ox\" value=\"162\" autocomplete=\"off\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"asea-filter-option-label\">Using Youtube in JARVEE<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/label>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>                                \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/fieldset>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t<!----- Search Box Results ------>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"asea_search_results\"><\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/form>\r\n\r\n\t\t<\/div>\t\t<\/section>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t<!-------- ASEA Sub Section Container 1-3 --------------->\r\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"asea-sub-section-1-3\"><\/section>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t<!-------- ASEA Sub Section Container 1-4 --------------->\r\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"asea-sub-section-1-4\"><\/section>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t<!-------- ASEA Sub Section Container 1-5 --------------->\r\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"asea-sub-section-1-5\"><\/section>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/section>\r\n\r\n\t\t<\/div>\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<div id=\"eckb-article-body\">  <div id=\"eckb-article-left-sidebar\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t        <article id=\"eckb-article-content\" data-article-id=\"4799\" >                        <div id=\"eckb-article-content-header\"><div class=\"eckb-article-title kb-article-id\" id=\"4799\"><\/div><div class=\"eckb-article-content-header__article-meta\"><div class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__date-created\"><span class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__date-created__date-icon epkbfa epkbfa-calendar\"><\/span><span class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__date-created__text\">Created On<\/span><span class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__date-created__date\"><time class=\"entry-date\" datetime=\"2019-06-30T11:35:01+00:00\">June 30, 2019<\/time><\/span><\/div><div class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__author\"><span class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__author__author-icon epkbfa epkbfa-user\"><\/span><span class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__author__text\">by<\/span><span class=\"eckb-ach__article-meta__author__name\">Elaina M<\/span><\/div><\/div>\r\n<div class=\"eckb-breadcrumb\" style=\"padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; font-size:14px;;\">\t\t\t<div class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-label\">\r\n\t\t\tYou are here:\t\t<\/div>\t\t<nav class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-outline\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\">\r\n\t\t<ul class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-nav\">       <li style=\"font-size:14px;;\">\t<span class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-link\"><a tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/knowledge-base\/\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\" >KB Home<\/span><\/a><span class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-link-icon ep_font_icon_right_arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/span>\t<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size:14px;;\">\t<span class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-link\"><a tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/knowledge-base\/category\/using-the-linkedin-platform\/\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\" >Using LinkedIn in JARVEE<\/span><\/a><span class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-link-icon ep_font_icon_right_arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/span>\t<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size:14px;;\">\t<span class=\"eckb-breadcrumb-link\"><span aria-current=\"page\"style=\"color: #000000;\" >LinkedIn Accept Connection Requests<\/span>\t<\/span><\/li>\t\t<\/ul>\r\n\t<\/nav>\r\n\r\n<\/div>          <\/div><div id=\"eckb-article-content-body\"><p>In growing your Linkedin network, sending connection request is equally important as accepting them.\u00a0 Thus, if you are looking to automate this process, you can use Jarvee to avoid the hassle of manually accepting the requests.<\/p>\n<h2>How to automatically accept requests in Jarvee?<\/h2>\n<p>You can make use of the Accept Connection Requests tool.\u00a0 To access this tool, just go to TOOLS page &gt; click the Linkedin account where you want to run the tool &gt; click Accept Connection Requests from the left sub-menu<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5591\" src=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connections.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"496\" height=\"405\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connections.png 700w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connections-300x245.png 300w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connections-600x490.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 496px) 100vw, 496px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Setting up the tool:<\/h3>\n<p>This tool is very easy to use. And just like most Jarvee tools, you start with configuring the <strong>Run Timers<\/strong> which controls the behavior of the tool.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5595\" src=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connection-Request-Settings.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"705\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connection-Request-Settings.png 1205w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connection-Request-Settings-300x222.png 300w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connection-Request-Settings-768x569.png 768w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connection-Request-Settings-1024x759.png 1024w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Accept-Connection-Request-Settings-600x445.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 705px) 100vw, 705px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>1. Wait Between X and Y minutes before each operation<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>This is the interval that the tool will wait before it starts a new operation.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>2. Accept between X and Y connection requests for each operation<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can change the numbers here depending on how many connection requests would you like to accept in each operation.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>3. Execute Between X and Y<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Indicate the hours when you want the tool to operate.<\/li>\n<li>You can\u00a0 &#8216;add an interval&#8217; for the execution hours as well as &#8216;randomize intervals daily&#8217;.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>4. Days of the week when to operate<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Select or check the days when the tool will execute actions.<\/li>\n<li>You may opt to rotate the days and Jarvee would pick the equivalent number of days you have initially selected. The selection is random and you have the option to exclude weekends in the variation in case you don\u2019t want the tool to execute during those days.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Additional Options:<\/h3>\n<p>5. Send a Message to the accepted connections<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can check this option if you want to send a message after you have accepted a connection request.<\/li>\n<li>There are different TOKENS you use on your message and it will be replaced by corresponding user information.<\/li>\n<li>Please note that you need to activate the <a href=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/knowledge-base\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> tool &gt; Send Messages tab to start sending messages.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>6. Secondary Messages<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use this if you want to send a second message when the user has replied OR has not replied after the initial message was sent.<\/li>\n<li>You can set how many times it will retry.<\/li>\n<li>There is also an option to Edit Secondary Messages.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&#x1f4a1;\u00a0 You can click on the &#8220;How It Works&#8221; button to know more about how the option to secondary messages works.<\/p>\n<h3>Accepted Requests table:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>From this table, you will see all the accepted requests.<\/li>\n<li>You have the option to click Browse which when clicked will open a browser and go to the profile of the accepted user<\/li>\n<li>The Copy action will copy the profile link of the user<\/li>\n<li>You can replicate the settings to other Linkedin Accept tool by clicking the Copy Settings button<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4809\" src=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Linkedin-Accept-Connection-Requests-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"664\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Linkedin-Accept-Connection-Requests-2.png 920w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Linkedin-Accept-Connection-Requests-2-300x113.png 300w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Linkedin-Accept-Connection-Requests-2-768x288.png 768w, https:\/\/jarvee.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Linkedin-Accept-Connection-Requests-2-600x225.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 664px) 100vw, 664px\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div><div id=\"eckb-article-content-footer\">\r\n\t\t <div class=\"epkb-article-navigation-container \">            \t\t\t\t  <div class=\"epkb-article-navigation__previous\">\r\n\t\t\t\t  <a href=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/knowledge-base\/linkedin-endorse-connections-tool\/\" >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"epkb-article-navigation__label\">Previous<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span title=\"LinkedIn Endorse Connections Tool\" class=\"epkb-article-navigation-article__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"epkb-article-navigation__previous__icon epkbfa ep_font_icon_document\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLinkedIn Endorse Connections Tool\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/a>\t\t\t\t  <\/div>                \t\t\t\t  <div class=\"epkb-article-navigation__next\">\r\n\t\t\t\t  <a href=\"https:\/\/jarvee.com\/knowledge-base\/full-browser-experience\/?seq_no=3\" >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"epkb-article-navigation__label\">Next<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span title=\"Full Browser Experience\" class=\"epkb-article-navigation-article__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tFull Browser Experience\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"epkb-article-navigation__next__icon epkbfa ep_font_icon_document\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/a>\r\n\t\t\t   \t\t\t\t  <\/div> \r\n\t\t <\/div>        <\/div>\r\n\t\t        <\/article><!-- \/#eckb-article-content -->     <div id=\"eckb-article-right-sidebar\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/#eckb-article-body -->              <div id=\"eckb-article-footer\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div><!-- \/#eckb-a